Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.75,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cold, I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:27.04,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll drink some warm milk...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:30.77,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:35.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,There's a nice smell \Ncoming from the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:47.90,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan, Aki-chan, Aki-chan, Aki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:24.99,sign_3357_7_The_Place_We_Lon,Title,0000,0000,0000,,The Place We Longed to Reach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:30.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mayu-chan, what are you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.50,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.93,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepping for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:37.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A-At this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:41.10,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you're acting kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:45.07,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You were muttering the landlady's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:47.27,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:50.49,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you must be half-asleep \Nand hearing things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.52,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:55.79,Main Dialogue Top,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, right now! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.79,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's hiding something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.28,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what you're making.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:00.28,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:04.58,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! It's a secret until tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.16,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You can't look! You can't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:12.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute, I can't pursue it any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:13.92,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go talk to Kuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:17.92,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.78,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan, are you still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.05,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I sure am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:26.06,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, Mayu-chan was muttering \Nthe landlady's name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.92,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while dressed like a witch \Nand stirring a big pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.81,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,C-Calm down! What on Earth happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:39.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan was muttering the landlady's name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.49,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while making something in a big pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:45.16,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been the kind of \Ncreepy potion that witches make!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.96,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,A creepy potion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Like a paralyzing potion...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.54,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.54,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,C-Creepy potion...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.87,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go sneak a taste of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.42,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:05.93,Italics Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Nisn't tomorrow Valentine's Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Will the landlady be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.56,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What if there's some kind of incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What if we wake up in the morning \Nto find the landlady unconscious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.69,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like the premise \Nof a mystery novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:24.20,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say, for example, the landlady \Ndoesn't wake up in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.10,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,So we go to her room to check on her, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:34.18,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,And we find her in the middle of changing, \Nin a very immodest position!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:39.42,sign_6617_52_Hitotose,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hitotose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:47.18,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried about the landlady, \NI couldn't get any sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.93,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hina-chan. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Landlady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:56.21,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You look a bit pale. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.94,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.15,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What now? Where should I even start?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:08.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please take extra good care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:11.10,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.58,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.83,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.89,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.46,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for doing this every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.67,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Landlady! \NI'll check it for poison first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:23.84,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.47,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I've got some for you, too, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:31.47,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something to make you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:34.45,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're just Valentine's \Nchocolates, Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.73,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:42.96,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan and I were making chocolates \Nto serve at the coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But why were you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.89,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It was really cold last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.24,sign_8363_74_Dressed__Warmly,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Dressed \NWarmly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:51.24,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It made cooking so uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:55.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,And why were you muttering \Nthe landlady's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.62,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.68,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I heard if you chant the name of the person\N you're making chocolate for,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:01.49,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,it'll taste better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:04.00,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it written in a book of spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.14,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure you were making \Nsome kind of potion to paralyze the landlady!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:14.52,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, you come up with \Nsome of the most outlandish insults...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.90,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I made this chocolate for Chiaki-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.02,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,but will I be able to give it to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.41,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:34.16,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.96,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I really admire you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:39.16,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:47.92,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.84,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it all planned out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.68,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.45,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.69,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,R-Reality is harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.69,Main Dialogue Top,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.20,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,If I hesitate too long, I'll miss my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:13.97,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.16,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.71,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yua-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:20.92,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.34,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:30.09,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.41,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:35.14,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Now that she's right in front of me, \NI'm so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.16,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to give it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Landlady! Happy Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:43.49,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I bought this at the school store!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:45.30,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.39,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you've got lots of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:49.11,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:53.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so mentally strong \Nonly at times like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:55.74,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.99,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:02.10,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me. \NI want your help with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.25,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.51,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give chocolate to Chiaki-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:10.01,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,but when I try to be honest about \Nhow I feel, I get embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.08,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought her behavior \Nmade it obvious enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.04,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:21.71,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Yua-chan, have you not been able to \Ngive your chocolate to Aki-chan yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:22.14,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:25.77,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you know I'm giving it to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.97,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have ESP?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.03,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty obvious just from watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.24,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.54,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.65,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair accessory is crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.79,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:48.53,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan's pretty, and really nice to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.92,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Even the girls love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.05,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I see... That's very true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.85,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:58.34,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she saved me when I was \Nsurrounded by older students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:58.93,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.47,Flashback Dialogue,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.15,Flashback Dialogue,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:09.92,Flashback Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:10.57,Flashback Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.85,Flashback Dialogue,GirlC,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Who the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.07,Flashback Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan! You came for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:17.45,Flashback Dialogue,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:25.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,In spite of how she looks, is the landlady \Nactually a delinquent at heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:27.08,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:30.09,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It was my first day of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:32.64,Flashback Dialogue,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,You're so tiny and cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.55,Flashback Dialogue,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Are you new?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.34,Flashback Dialogue,GirlC,0000,0000,0000,,What's your class?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.57,Flashback Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:37.07,Flashback Dialogue,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.09,Flashback Dialogue,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Come here and I'll give you some candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.30,Flashback Dialogue,GirlC,0000,0000,0000,,Look, she's blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:44.56,Flashback Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you're making Mayu-chan uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.23,Flashback Dialogue,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you new, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.69,Flashback Dialogue,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,You're really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.24,Flashback Dialogue,GirlC,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair's so smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.79,Flashback Dialogue,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,And your figure's perfect! \NLook at that waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:56.24,Flashback Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, excuse me... I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.82,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how Aki-chan helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:03.12,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not easy being beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.62,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I get nervous whenever I see Senpai's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:11.50,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd like you to give her this for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.98,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.60,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You put all your heart into making it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,so you have to give it to her yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:21.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll understand your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.35,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:28.64,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I chanted \Nher name while I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:33.12,Flashback Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai, Chiaki-senpai, Chiaki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:40.53,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she read \Nthe same book Mayu-chan did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.43,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.29,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.12,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.70,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:01.84,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I've always watched you, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.80,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.93,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought we seemed \Nto make eye contact a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.67,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:11.41,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.97,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to give you something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.94,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come to the shop after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.94,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I really can?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:23.70,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Your expressions change at the \Ndrop of the hat. It's so neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:29.45,sign_16393_187_Coffee_Shop,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:33.71,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Senpai wants \Nto give me in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.71,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.11,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Have some chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.20,Main Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:41.86,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:44.10,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:47.72,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,We're giving chocolate \Nto all our customers today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.73,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan made them! \NCome in and have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.28,Italics Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai in a maid outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.49,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,What a feast for the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:03.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She was so happy, it made her cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:21.26,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,We sure had lots of customers \Nyesterday, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:26.27,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We gave away almost \Nall the chocolate I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:34.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,As the landlady, the boost in sales \Nyesterday makes me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:38.15,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It must be because of \Nyour chocolate, Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.86,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.53,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think it had more to do with how you and \NHina-chan looked in the maid outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.01,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Mayu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:48.66,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.16,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.65,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't have anything \Nplanned for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.79,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't call it thanking you \Nfor the Valentine's chocolate,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:01.92,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,but if you like, why don't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.93,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is Aki-chan asking me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:07.93,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:10.93,sign_18892_215_Chocolate_Rhapso,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate Rhapsody No. 8 \NOld Town Factory \NShimokita Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:14.25,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Tickets to a play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:17.19,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I got a bunch of them from a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:23.94,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted to invite all of you \Nas thanks for the Valentine's chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:27.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'd be happy to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:34.72,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan seems to be  \Npouting about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:36.82,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:40.46,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.47,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:51.10,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really into plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.35,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.37,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:02.36,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,The theater where this is \Nbeing held... is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:06.49,sign_18892_215_Chocolate_Rhapso,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shimokita Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:06.49,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... It says "Shimokita Theater."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:12.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the place where \Nwe want to perform, Suzuran, is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.82,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's near there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:19.37,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So when we go to see the play, \Ncan we also take a look at Suzuran?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.93,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, if we leave a bit early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:25.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.26,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm excited, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:30.80,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I bet there's a lot of great food \Naround there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.79,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} what you're excited for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.77,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:47.96,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuran...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:54.53,sign_21304_240_Closed_Today__So,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Closed Today \NSorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:58.57,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.17,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.42,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you decided to \Ncome along, Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.61,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:09.17,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was the one who told \NHina-chan about Suzuran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.08,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:13.55,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That was when we found our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:20.67,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're going to check out \NSuzuran before the play, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.06,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,So let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:25.63,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan, you didn't forget \Nthe tickets, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.19,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. All set.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.86,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan, you didn't forget to \Nlock up the bookstore, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.57,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:35.48,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:36.70,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.58,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lock the coffee shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.34,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there's no place to sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:51.78,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head more toward the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:12.18,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,You could just grab that rail...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:15.36,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! I can reach it on my tiptoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:18.49,Main Dialogue,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to have my seat, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.27,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.34,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like Mayu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:24.12,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:28.74,Main Dialogue,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,The train arriving now is the \Nexpress train bound for Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.20,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,This way. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:42.18,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,This sure is a complicated route.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.60,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:47.23,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,This station has been under \Nconstruction for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.52,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:02.64,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to get the exits \Nmixed up in this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:03.62,sign_24438_272_South_Exit_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,South Exit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:03.62,sign_24438_273_South_Exit_This_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,South Exit This Way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:03.62,sign_24438_274_Welcome_to__Shim,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to \NShimokitazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.62,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.00,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'd get lost here in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.17,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.38,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan isn't behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.38,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:18.68,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.02,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:29.31,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.34,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait just a second, Hina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.45,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to look for her ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.45,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,According to the map...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.46,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,She came downstairs with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.74,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's probably at the north exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.32,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.21,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:51.21,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,This is a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.12,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.59,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:03.60,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hina-chan? Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.62,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:10.61,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I went looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.38,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:19.03,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, why'd you move \Nwhen you were the one who got lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.64,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:23.19,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,No, Hina-chan, you did well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:24.87,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Kuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:28.66,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I got to buy up all the best food \Nfrom the shops around the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuu-chan, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:31.63,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.63,sign_26737_308_Honma_Theater_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Honma Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:41.14,sign_26797_309__Seki__Mini_Thea,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"Seki" Mini Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.58,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:48.89,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like we're seeing theaters everywhere \Njust by walking through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:52.85,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,This town is known as the "town of theater."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:54.27,sign_27067_313_Honma_Theater__T,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Honma Theater, The Suzuran, Train Station Mini Theater, \N"Seki" Mini Theater, Rakuen Mini Theater, Theater 717
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.27,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:59.49,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,And the one that started it all \Nis right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.28,sign_27334_317_Suzuran_Alley_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuran Alley
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.28,sign_27334_318_The_Suzuran_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Suzuran
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.28,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.53,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:10.29,sign_27442_321_Suzuran_Alley_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuran Alley
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:10.29,sign_27442_322_The_Suzuran_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Suzuran
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.63,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time seeing it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:10.29,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very classical-looking building.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.52,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:15.30,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'd love to take a look inside \Nif we ever have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:21.05,sign_27442_321_Suzuran_Alley_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuran Alley
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:21.05,sign_27700_328_The_Suzuran_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Suzuran
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:19.19,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so historical, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:21.05,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:25.68,Italics Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can stand on the stage \Nhere someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:50.46,Main Dialogue,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for coming today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.46,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you enjoy the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:58.97,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.09,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,I think I could learn a lot from that script.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:05.09,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I cried a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:08.02,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel really moved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.21,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,It moved you that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:13.23,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,It was a comedy. What part made you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:17.99,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,No way! The last part was really emotional!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:23.11,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,See? There's someone crying over there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:25.62,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.24,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.88,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:34.40,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.15,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.38,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:40.29,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,This really is quite a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:41.01,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:42.68,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.97,Main Dialogue,Mayuki,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're all here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.89,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we all go back to \Nthe coffee shop for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.73,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be all right if I joined you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:51.81,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:56.60,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fun to talk about \Nthe play over dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:59.19,Main Dialogue,Ruriko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sure it'll be a \Nproductive conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.44,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us, Yua-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:05.20,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, why are you all \Nhere with Chiaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.46,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yua-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:11.83,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I invited them all to \Nthank them for Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.96,Main Dialogue,Chiaki,0000,0000,0000,,I should have told you about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.46,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:20.59,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I've been theater-hopping \Nsince this morning, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:26.76,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,So you were moved to tears too, \Nhuh, Yua-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:30.47,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just had something \Nin my eyes, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:33.52,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a great play, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.15,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:38.05,Main Dialogue,Kuina,0000,0000,0000,,You two might actually \Nbe pretty similar, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.55,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:41.36,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,We are not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:45.90,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway... I wish I could've gone \Nto Suzuran with everyone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.48,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen it before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:49.69,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,I have, but I wanted to see it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:51.13,Main Dialogue,Hinako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:54.02,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? F-Fine.
